fulltitle: Anna Dereszowska – Maria de Buenos Aires with Anna and Piotr
title: Anna Dereszowska – Maria de Buenos Aires with Anna and Piotr
_filename: Anna Dereszowska – Maria de Buenos Aires with Anna and Piotr-yXs-PFx9bBs.mp4
description:
Anna Dereszowska sings “Maria de Buenos Aires” played live by Machina del Tango at the 5th Łódź Tango Salon Festival 2015 in Lodz, Poland. Dancing are Anna Iberszer and Piotr Woźniak.
